#: ../../R/rabbit-job.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Cambridge] A batch job that does little, if any, real work, but creates one"
" or more copies of itself, breeding like rabbits. Compare :ref:`wabbit`\\, "
":ref:`fork-bomb`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Cambridge] ほとんど、あるいはまったく実際の仕事をせず、自分自身のコピーを一つ以上作り、ウサギのように繁殖するバッチジョブ。\\ "
":ref:`wabbit`\\ 、\\ :ref:`fork-bomb`\\ と比較せよ。"
